data.description:
Welcome to 1727 Pierce Rd, a charming 2-bedroom, 1-bath home nestled on a quiet street in south Lansing.

As you step inside, the gleaming hardwood floors throughout and fresh paint. The recently updated kitchen and bathroom make it ready to move right in. Fresh paint throughout the interior enhances the home's appeal, creating a bright and airy atmosphere. The thoughtful layout maximizes space and functionality, making every room feel inviting and comfortable.

One of the standout features of this property is the expansive 1/2 acre lot, providing ample space for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the fresh air. The well-maintained yard is a canvas ready for your personal touch and landscaping dreams. For those with a passion for mechanics, the 2-car garage is a true gem. Equipped with a mechanics pit, this space is perfect for car enthusiasts or anyone who enjoys hands-on projects. Imagine the convenience of having your own dedicated space for vehicle maintenance or DIY endeavors. Contact us today for a private showing.
